            "name": "Ifrah Khan"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-06-28",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "A very good school for academics and co-curricular activity. I was a student in this school from class L.K.G to class 10 AISSCE 2020. Twelve years spent in this school.Nice environment, teachers are strict, discipline is maintained and good facilities of library, swimming pool, basketball, karate, computer classes and affordable canteen and high fees from class 9.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
