          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Poushali Dutta"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-05-21",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I've spent 13 yrs of my life here.. In 2017 I completed schooling from here.. Now I am a teacher in a CBSE school. But in these 6yrs I realise how my I miss my school. The spent the most golden period of my life here... My heart still lies there.. They have made me what I'm today. I shall always be thankful to this school and all the teachers who have guided me ❤",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
