          "reviewBody": "I wouldn't have given a single star.... worst school.... don't take admission here... most of the teachers are very rude here ... specially in class XI science stream teachers they harass the students ...... torcher the students.... if you want your child future to be secure please go for some other schools... there are many other good schools in kolkata but don't take admission here.... the teachers here destroys the students future .",
